Views.Name: VwApplicationEntry
Views.Definition:
SELECT ae."IdApplicationEntry",
    aet."IdApplicationEntryToken",
    aet."Token",
    aet."Version",
    aet."SourceFilePath",
    ae."AuditOperation",
    ae."Uri",
    aet."MethodInfo",
    aet."MainEntityName",
    ae."MainEntityIdentifier",
    aet."Description",
    ae."RuntimeUniqueKey",
    ae."CreatedUtc",
    ae."CorrelationId",
    ae."ExternalCorrelationId",
    ae."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    ei."ApplicationName"
   FROM (((aud."ApplicationEntry" ae
     JOIN aud."ApplicationEntryToken" aet ON ((ae."IdApplicationEntryToken" = aet."IdApplicationEntryToken")))
     LEFT JOIN usr."User" u ON ((ae."IdUser" = u."IdUser")))
     LEFT JOIN aud."EnvironmentInfo" ei ON ((ae."RuntimeUniqueKey" = ei."RuntimeUniqueKey")));

Views.Name: VwAuditEntry
Views.Definition:
SELECT ae."IdAuditEntry",
    ae."CreatedUtc",
    ae."IdAuditType",
    atp."Name" AS "AuditType",
    ae."TableName",
    ae."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    ae."PrimaryKey",
    ae."OldValues",
    ae."NewValues",
    ae."AffectedColumns",
    ae."AuditCorrelationId",
    ae."CommandQueryName",
    ae."IdCommandQuery",
    ae."CorrelationId"
   FROM ((aud."AuditEntry" ae
     JOIN aud."AuditType" atp ON ((ae."IdAuditType" = atp."ItemCode")))
     LEFT JOIN usr."User" u ON ((ae."IdUser" = u."IdUser")));

Views.Name: VwCommandQueryEntry
Views.Definition:
SELECT ent."IdCommandQueryEntry",
    ent."CreatedUtc",
    ent."CommandQueryName",
    ent."TraceFrame",
    ent."IsQuery",
    ent."IdUser",
    ent."CorrelationId",
    ex."ElapsedMilliseconds",
    ex."IsError",
    ex."Data" AS "ResponseData"
   FROM (aud."CommandQueryEntry" ent
     LEFT JOIN aud."CommandQueryExit" ex ON ((ent."IdCommandQueryEntry" = ex."IdCommandQueryExit")));

Views.Name: VwLog
Views.Definition:
SELECT l."IdLog",
    l."IdLogLevel",
    ll."Name" AS "LogLevel",
    l."CreatedUtc",
    l."InternalMessage",
    l."Detail",
    l."StackTrace",
    l."MethodCallId",
    l."SourceContext",
    l."CorrelationId",
    l."RuntimeUniqueKey",
    l."IsDbLog",
    ei."ApplicationName"
   FROM ((aud."Log" l
     JOIN aud."LogLevel" ll ON ((l."IdLogLevel" = ll."ItemCode")))
     LEFT JOIN aud."EnvironmentInfo" ei ON ((l."RuntimeUniqueKey" = ei."RuntimeUniqueKey")));

Views.Name: VwLogMessage
Views.Definition:
SELECT lm."IdLogMessage",
    lm."IdLogLevel",
    ll."Name" AS "LogLevel",
    lm."CreatedUtc",
    lm."RuntimeUniqueKey",
    lm."CorrelationId",
    lm."SourceSystemName",
    "substring"(lm."InternalMessage", 1, 100) AS "InternalMessage",
    "substring"(lm."ClientMessage", 1, 100) AS "ClientMessage",
    "substring"(lm."Detail", 1, 100) AS "Detail",
    "substring"(lm."StackTrace", 1, 100) AS "StackTrace",
    "substring"(lm."TraceFrame", 1, 100) AS "TraceFrame",
    lm."LogCode",
    lm."MethodCallId",
    lm."SourceContext",
    lm."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    lm."CommandQueryName",
    lm."IdCommandQuery",
    lm."MethodCallElapsedMilliseconds",
    lm."IsValidationError",
    lm."PropertyName",
    lm."DisplayPropertyName",
    "substring"(lm."ValidationFailure", 1, 100) AS "ValidationFailure",
    "substring"(lm."ContextProperties", 1, 100) AS "ContextProperties",
    lm."Tags",
    ei."ApplicationName"
   FROM (((aud."LogMessage" lm
     JOIN aud."LogLevel" ll ON ((lm."IdLogLevel" = ll."ItemCode")))
     LEFT JOIN usr."User" u ON ((lm."IdUser" = u."IdUser")))
     LEFT JOIN aud."EnvironmentInfo" ei ON ((lm."RuntimeUniqueKey" = ei."RuntimeUniqueKey")));

Views.Name: VwRequestsAndResponses
Views.Definition:
SELECT req."IdRequest",
    res."IdResponse",
    req."RuntimeUniqueKey",
    req."CreatedUtc" AS "Request_CreatedUtc",
    res."CreatedUtc" AS "Response_CreatedUtc",
    req."CorrelationId",
    req."ExternalCorrelationId" AS "Request_ExternalCorrelationId",
    res."ExternalCorrelationId" AS "Response_ExternalCorrelationId",
    res."StatusCode",
    req."Method",
    req."Path",
    req."QueryString",
    req."Protocol",
    req."Scheme",
    req."Host",
    req."RemoteIp",
    "substring"(req."Headers", 1, 100) AS "Request_Headers",
    "substring"(res."Headers", 1, 100) AS "Response_Headers",
    req."ContentType" AS "Request_ContentType",
    res."ContentType" AS "Response_ContentType",
    res."ElapsedMilliseconds" AS "Response_ElapsedMilliseconds",
    "substring"(req."Form", 1, 100) AS "Form",
    "substring"(req."Body", 1, 100) AS "Request_Body",
    "substring"(res."Body", 1, 100) AS "Response_Body",
    "substring"(res."Error", 1, 100) AS "Response_Error",
    ei."ApplicationName"
   FROM ((aud."Request" req
     LEFT JOIN aud."Response" res ON (((req."CorrelationId" = res."CorrelationId") AND (req."RuntimeUniqueKey" = res."RuntimeUniqueKey"))))
     LEFT JOIN aud."EnvironmentInfo" ei ON ((req."RuntimeUniqueKey" = ei."RuntimeUniqueKey")));

Views.Name: VwPermission
Views.Definition:
SELECT p."IdPermission",
    p."Code",
    p."Name",
    p."Description",
    p."IsSystemPermission"
   FROM usr."Permission" p;

Views.Name: VwRole
Views.Definition:
SELECT r."IdRole",
    r."Name",
    r."HasFixedPermissions",
    r."HasFixedUsers",
    r."IsSystemRole",
    r."DeletedUtc"
   FROM usr."Role" r;

Views.Name: VwUser
Views.Definition:
SELECT u."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    u."Email",
    u."IsSystemUser",
    u."LockoutEndUtc",
    u."DeletedUtc"
   FROM usr."User" u;

Views.Name: VwUserPermission
Views.Definition:
SELECT rp."IdRolePermission",
    NULL::uuid AS "IdUserPermission",
    p."IdPermission",
    p."IsSystemPermission",
    r."IdRole",
    r."Name" AS "Role_Name",
    r."HasFixedPermissions",
    r."HasFixedUsers",
    r."IsSystemRole",
    ur."IdUserRole",
    ur."IdUserTenant",
    t."IdTenant",
    t."Name" AS "Tenant",
    u."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    u."Email",
    u."IsSystemUser",
    u."LockoutEndUtc"
   FROM ((((((usr."RolePermission" rp
     JOIN usr."Permission" p ON ((rp."IdPermission" = p."IdPermission")))
     JOIN usr."Role" r ON (((rp."IdRole" = r."IdRole") AND (r."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     JOIN usr."UserRole" ur ON (((r."IdRole" = ur."IdRole") AND (ur."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     JOIN usr."User" u ON (((ur."IdUser" = u."IdUser") AND (u."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     LEFT JOIN usr."UserTenant" ut ON (((ur."IdUserTenant" = ut."IdUserTenant") AND (ut."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     LEFT JOIN usr."Tenant" t ON (((ut."IdTenant" = t."IdTenant") AND (t."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
  WHERE (rp."DeletedUtc" IS NULL)
UNION ALL
 SELECT NULL::uuid AS "IdRolePermission",
    up."IdUserPermission",
    p."IdPermission",
    p."IsSystemPermission",
    NULL::uuid AS "IdRole",
    NULL::character varying AS "Role_Name",
    NULL::boolean AS "HasFixedPermissions",
    NULL::boolean AS "HasFixedUsers",
    NULL::boolean AS "IsSystemRole",
    NULL::uuid AS "IdUserRole",
    up."IdUserTenant",
    t."IdTenant",
    t."Name" AS "Tenant",
    u."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    u."Email",
    u."IsSystemUser",
    u."LockoutEndUtc"
   FROM ((((usr."UserPermission" up
     JOIN usr."User" u ON (((up."IdUser" = u."IdUser") AND (u."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     JOIN usr."Permission" p ON ((up."IdPermission" = p."IdPermission")))
     LEFT JOIN usr."UserTenant" ut ON (((up."IdUserTenant" = ut."IdUserTenant") AND (ut."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     LEFT JOIN usr."Tenant" t ON (((ut."IdTenant" = t."IdTenant") AND (t."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
  WHERE (up."DeletedUtc" IS NULL);

Views.Name: VwUserRole
Views.Definition:
SELECT ur."IdUserRole",
    ur."IdUserTenant",
    t."IdTenant",
    t."Name" AS "Tenant",
    u."IdUser",
    u."Login",
    u."Email",
    u."IsSystemUser",
    u."LockoutEndUtc",
    r."IdRole",
    r."Name" AS "Role_Name",
    r."HasFixedPermissions",
    r."HasFixedUsers",
    r."IsSystemRole"
   FROM ((((usr."UserRole" ur
     JOIN usr."User" u ON (((ur."IdUser" = u."IdUser") AND (u."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     JOIN usr."Role" r ON (((ur."IdRole" = r."IdRole") AND (r."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     LEFT JOIN usr."UserTenant" ut ON (((ur."IdUserTenant" = ut."IdUserTenant") AND (ut."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
     LEFT JOIN usr."Tenant" t ON (((ut."IdTenant" = t."IdTenant") AND (t."DeletedUtc" IS NULL))))
  WHERE (ur."DeletedUtc" IS NULL);
